minidlna (1.1.4-netgear4) stable; urgency=low

  * Use "Album Artist" tag from AAC files.
  * Improve image resize quality at the edges.
  * Handle StartingIndex on magic containers.
  * Properly escape episode titles from nfo files.
  * Fix TiVo title and description escaping.
  * Don't honor the NO_RESIZE flag for thumbnails.

